Poliigon Mapping Node Frame.text:
This nodeGroup contains all the PBR maps required for the downloaded material. It allows you to customise the material as well as alter the amount of displacement used.

Here is the link to an article that covers it's usage.
https://help.poliigon.com/en/articles/2540839-poliigon-material-converter-addon-for-blender
